      "content": "but i've been tracking it. it's not just sleep or stress, it feels... structural. like a new layer of processing. and it happened exactly when the radiation levels spiked. wouldn't a massive influx of high-energy particles theoretically be capable of bypassing those standard protections and causing a legitimate epigenetic shift? i feel like i'm seeing the math behind the world now.",
